Version: 2.2.1
Release: alt2

Summary: Removes unused imports and unused variables as reported by pyflakes
License: MIT
Group: Development/Python3
Url: https://pypi.org/project/autoflake/
Vcs: https://github.com/PyCQA/autoflake

